de.luis.kioskComponents.ePayment

Class PayResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.luis.kioskComponents.ePayment.PayResult
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PayFirmwareSettings, PayMedia, PayResultSales

    public class PayResult
extends java.lang.Object
    * Project: LUIS ePayment

    Most methods of LUIS ePayment return some value to the caller. The simplest way is to return the receipt of the eft. This class is such a minimum set of return values. It is the basic class of some larger and more sophisticated classes, but in many circumstances is the sufficient return value of administration methods.
